		</short>
		<long>
			<en>
							<![CDATA[
Kanban Looks Good is a visual enhancement plugin for the GLPI Project Kanban module.  
It adds automatic display of:

- **Priority badge** (same format and colors as GLPI core)
- **Planned Duration** (for both Projects and Project Tasks)
- **Soft background color** based on project priority
- Non-intrusive UI improvements without modifying GLPI core

This plugin aims to improve clarity, visibility and project management efficiency in daily use.
							]]>
					</en>
		</long>
